==============================================================================
Desired Performance Data
==============================================================================

  1. PER vs. SNR vs. RMS delay-spread
  2. FDR vs. SNR vs. RMS delay-spread

==============================================================================
Experiments for INFCOM 2012
==============================================================================

  1. awgn - TGn CM-A with no fading (i.e. AWGN)
  2. cfo - carrier frequency offset (13.675 ppm)
  3. freq - frequency selective fading (TGn CM-D w/o time selective fading)
  4. fading - time and frequency selective fading (complete TGn CM-D)
  5. tcpack - short packet (TCP ACK size = 40 bytes)

==============================================================================
Subdirectories
==============================================================================
Important subdirectories for experiments:

  * rawdata/ -raw trace files
  * parsedata/ - parsed data files (unformatted)
  * paperdata/ - formatted data used to create graphs in papers
